title: Intro-duction
info:
From "Decycled" by Vectra, also called [url=http://bitworld.bitfellas.org/demo.php?id=7316]"Recycled"[/url]

"hai.
i am louis armstrong
or at least grade
wants me to say so.
excuses forever:

bloody afternoons.
